reviewText: Video box liner notes - "An intimate portrait of the women and men who have dedicated their lives to creating perfect bodies. This behind the scenes look will reveal the secrets and desires of those who aspire to attain the magnificence of the ultimate body form.  It's a close up view of beautiful women and masculine men as they take you through vigorous workouts and training sessions; you'll discover the untold hours necessary to prepare for competition in the world of bodybuilding."
